                    </note>
<note type="date" xml:id="date">
<p>Like <ref target="let729.xml">letter 729</ref> to Theo, this letter was written on Friday, 4 January 1889. This was, after all, the day of Vincent’s ‘first trip out of the hospital’ <ref target="#l-2">(ll. 2-3)</ref>. <ref target="let729.xml">See letter 729</ref>, <hi rend="ital">Date</hi>.</p>
                    </note>
<note type="additionalDetail" xml:id="additionalDetail">
<p>Written in pencil on the back of <ref target="let729.xml">letter 729</ref> to Theo. It is not certain whether Theo let Gauguin read the letter in this form or whether he made a copy for him.</p>
